      "message": "Purge \u003d remove user\u0027s CQ vote without starting a Run.\n\nProblem: in the two use cases described in storage.proto,\nstatus quo is CV trying to create a new Run, failing, because Run with this ID already exists, and scheduling a retry. Example: https://screenshot.googleplex.com/euNWRURbwzjdBJA\n\nProposed solution: don\u0027t retry, but detect such case and purge the CL as invalid,\ninviting user to re-trigger if necessary.\n\nDoes this help?",
